</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>BECOME THE ULTIMATE SUPPORT!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041200/extras/eee837579a5e6f60d3313a061f73996f.poster.avif?t=1761210149\" width=800 height=462 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041200/extras/eee837579a5e6f60d3313a061f73996f.webm?t=1761210149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041200/extras/eee837579a5e6f60d3313a061f73996f.mp4?t=1761210149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Organise your party, meet new characters and help them to survive this legendary quest!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>FALL IN LOVE WITH YOUR 9 COMPANIONS!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041200/extras/a5d2e9cbbacc238ba53f669dbe118f50.poster.avif?t=1761210149\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041200/extras/a5d2e9cbbacc238ba53f669dbe118f50.webm?t=1761210149\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3041200/extras/a5d2e9cbbacc238ba53f669dbe118f50.mp4?t=1761210149\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Help save the world in this light-hearted character-driven story!</p>",
